TDD - Class in com.coreconsulting.res.openehr.tdd2canonical
This class implements functionality related to TDD handling, such as deserializing it from a XML instance, resolving the openEHR namespace prefix, @template_id and associated TDS, generic node manipulation and transformation to an openEHR Reference Model composition.

TDDTest - Class in com.coreconsulting.res.openehr.tdd2canonical
This class tests the TDD functionality, ranging from creating an instance from a serialized XML document, processing the @template_id, locating the associated TDS (from the local cache or a remote location) and transforming it to a composition that complies to the openEHR Reference Model XML schemas.
